                  VETERINARIANS
                </h2>

                <div class="card-body">
                  <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-image">
                      <img src="/images/profile-icon1.png" alt="" />
                    </div>
                    <p class="name">Dr. Francis M. Katalbas</p>
                    <p class="contact_num">
                      <b>Contact Number:</b> (0917)815-3121
                    </p>
                    <p class="email_address">
                      <b>Email:</b> DOKFMK@yahoo.com.ph
                    </p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-image">
                      <img src="/images/profile-icon2.png" alt="" />
                    </div>
                    <p class="name">Dr. Francisella P. Katalbas</p>
                    <p class="contact_num">
                      <b>Contact Number:</b> (0928)831-0031
                    </p>
                    <p class="email_address">
                      <b>Email:</b> franskatalbas@gmail.com
                    </p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-image">
                      <img src="/images/profile-icon3.png" alt="" />
                    </div>
                    <p class="name">Jessica Katalbas</p>
                    <p class="contact_num">
                      <b>Contact Number:</b> (0919)362-4915
                    </p>
                    <p class="email_address">
                      <b>Email:</b> jessicakatalbas@yahoo.com
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td
              colspan="6"
              style="
                color: white;
                text-align: center;
                vertical-align: middle;
                height: 200px;
                padding-left: 100px;
                padding-right: 100px;
              "
            >
              <h2 style="margin: 0 0 50px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 24px">
                We hope you enjoy visiting our website and learning more about
                our JPK Veterinary Clinic. We urge you to contact Dr. Katalbas
                or any other member of our team if you have any questions,
                concerns, or are ready to schedule your pet's visit with us! Be
                sure to reference our available services if you want to further
                discuss your pet's health and the treatment plan we'll be
                working on creating together. Our team here at JPK Veterinary
                Clinic look forward to meeting you and your incredible pet!
              </h2>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </center>
    </div>

    <script>
      function handleRegisterClick() {
        localStorage.setItem("isRegisterClicked", "true");
      }
    </script>
